509CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q31_t clip_q63_to_q31(
510 q63_t x)
511{
512 return ((q31_t) (x >> 32) != ((q31_t) x >> 31)) ?
513 ((0x7FFFFFFF ^ ((q31_t) (x >> 63)))) : (q31_t) x;
514}
515
519CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q15_t clip_q63_to_q15(
520 q63_t x)
521{
522 return ((q31_t) (x >> 32) != ((q31_t) x >> 31)) ?
523 ((0x7FFF ^ ((q15_t) (x >> 63)))) : (q15_t) (x >> 15);
524}
525
529CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q7_t clip_q31_to_q7(
530 q31_t x)
531{
532 return ((q31_t) (x >> 24) != ((q31_t) x >> 23)) ?
533 ((0x7F ^ ((q7_t) (x >> 31)))) : (q7_t) x;
534}
535
539CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q15_t clip_q31_to_q15(
540 q31_t x)
541{
542 return ((q31_t) (x >> 16) != ((q31_t) x >> 15)) ?
543 ((0x7FFF ^ ((q15_t) (x >> 31)))) : (q15_t) x;
544}

550CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q63_t mult32x64(
551 q63_t x,
552 q31_t y)
553{
554 return ((((q63_t) (x & 0x00000000FFFFFFFF) * y) >> 32) +
555 (((q63_t) (x >> 32) * y)));

568CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t __CLZ(
569 q31_t data)
570{
571 uint32_t count = 0;
572 uint32_t mask = 0x80000000;
573
574 while ((data & mask) == 0) {
575 count += 1u;
576 mask = mask >> 1u;
577 }
578
579 return (count);
580}

587CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t arm_recip_q31(
588 q31_t in,
589 q31_t* dst,
590 q31_t* pRecipTable)
591{
592 q31_t out;
593 uint32_t tempVal;
594 uint32_t index, i;
595 uint32_t signBits;
596
597 if (in > 0) {
598 signBits = ((uint32_t) (__CLZ( in) - 1));
599 }
600 else {
601 signBits = ((uint32_t) (__CLZ(-in) - 1));
602 }
603
604 /* Convert input sample to 1.31 format */
605 in = (in << signBits);
606
607 /* calculation of index for initial approximated Val */
608 index = (uint32_t)(in >> 24);
609 index = (index & INDEX_MASK);
610
611 /* 1.31 with exp 1 */
612 out = pRecipTable[index];
613
614 /* calculation of reciprocal value */
615 /* running approximation for two iterations */
616 for (i = 0u; i < 2u; i++) {
617 tempVal = (uint32_t) (((q63_t) in * out) >> 31);
618 tempVal = 0x7FFFFFFFu - tempVal;
619 /* 1.31 with exp 1 */
620 /* out = (q31_t) (((q63_t) out * tempVal) >> 30); */
621 out = clip_q63_to_q31(((q63_t) out * tempVal) >> 30);
622 }
623
624 /* write output */
625 *dst = out;
626
627 /* return num of signbits of out = 1/in value */
628 return (signBits + 1u);
629}

635CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t arm_recip_q15(
636 q15_t in,
637 q15_t* dst,
638 q15_t* pRecipTable)
639{
640 q15_t out = 0;
641 uint32_t tempVal = 0;
642 uint32_t index = 0, i = 0;
643 uint32_t signBits = 0;
644
645 if (in > 0) {
646 signBits = ((uint32_t)(__CLZ( in) - 17));
647 }
648 else {
649 signBits = ((uint32_t)(__CLZ(-in) - 17));
650 }
651
652 /* Convert input sample to 1.15 format */
653 in = (in << signBits);
654
655 /* calculation of index for initial approximated Val */
656 index = (uint32_t)(in >> 8);
657 index = (index & INDEX_MASK);
658
659 /* 1.15 with exp 1 */
660 out = pRecipTable[index];
661
662 /* calculation of reciprocal value */
663 /* running approximation for two iterations */
664 for (i = 0u; i < 2u; i++) {
665 tempVal = (uint32_t) (((q31_t) in * out) >> 15);
666 tempVal = 0x7FFFu - tempVal;
667 /* 1.15 with exp 1 */
668 out = (q15_t) (((q31_t) out * tempVal) >> 14);
669 /* out = clip_q31_to_q15(((q31_t) out * tempVal) >> 14); */
670 }
671
672 /* write output */
673 *dst = out;
674
675 /* return num of signbits of out = 1/in value */
676 return (signBits + 1);
677}

683#if defined(ARM_MATH_CM0_FAMILY)
684CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q31_t __SSAT(
685 q31_t x,
686 uint32_t y)
687{
688 int32_t posMax, negMin;
689 uint32_t i;
690
691 posMax = 1;
692 for (i = 0; i < (y - 1); i++) {
693 posMax = posMax * 2;
694 }
695
696 if (x > 0) {
697 posMax = (posMax - 1);
698
699 if (x > posMax) {
700 x = posMax;
701 }
702 }
703 else {
704 negMin = -posMax;
705
706 if (x < negMin) {
707 x = negMin;
708 }
709 }
710 return (x);
711}
712#endif /* end of ARM_MATH_CM0_FAMILY */

721/*
722 * @brief C custom defined QADD8 for M3 and M0 processors
723 */
724CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t __QADD8(
725 uint32_t x,
726 uint32_t y)
727{
728 q31_t r, s, t, u;
729
730 r = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 24) >> 24) + (((q31_t)y << 24) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
731 s = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 16) >> 24) + (((q31_t)y << 16) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
732 t = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 8) >> 24) + (((q31_t)y << 8) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
733 u = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x ) >> 24) + (((q31_t)y ) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
734
735 return ((uint32_t)((u << 24) | (t << 16) | (s << 8) | (r )));
736}

740 * @brief C custom defined QSUB8 for M3 and M0 processors
741 */
742CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE uint32_t __QSUB8(
743 uint32_t x,
744 uint32_t y)
745{

747
748 r = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 24) >> 24) - (((q31_t)y << 24) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
749 s = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 16) >> 24) - (((q31_t)y << 16) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
750 t = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x << 8) >> 24) - (((q31_t)y << 8) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
751 u = __SSAT(((((q31_t)x ) >> 24) - (((q31_t)y ) >> 24)), 8) & (int32_t)0x000000FF;
752
753 return ((uint32_t)((u << 24) | (t << 16) | (s << 8) | (r )));
754}

4786CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE float32_t arm_pid_f32(
4787 arm_pid_instance_f32* S,
4788 float32_t in)
4789{
4790 float32_t out;
4791
4792 /* y[n] = y[n-1] + A0 * x[n] + A1 * x[n-1] + A2 * x[n-2] */
4793 out = (S->A0 * in) +
4794 (S->A1 * S->state[0]) + (S->A2 * S->state[1]) + (S->state[2]);
4795
4796 /* Update state */
4797 S->state[1] = S->state[0];
4798 S->state[0] = in;
4799 S->state[2] = out;
4800
4801 /* return to application */
4802 return (out);
4803
4804}
4805
4820CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q31_t arm_pid_q31(
4821 arm_pid_instance_q31* S,
4822 q31_t in)
4823{
4824 q63_t acc;
4825 q31_t out;
4826
4827 /* acc = A0 * x[n] */
4828 acc = (q63_t) S->A0 * in;
4829
4830 /* acc += A1 * x[n-1] */
4831 acc += (q63_t) S->A1 * S->state[0];
4832
4833 /* acc += A2 * x[n-2] */
4834 acc += (q63_t) S->A2 * S->state[1];
4835
4836 /* convert output to 1.31 format to add y[n-1] */
4837 out = (q31_t) (acc >> 31u);
4838
4839 /* out += y[n-1] */
4840 out += S->state[2];
4841
4842 /* Update state */
4843 S->state[1] = S->state[0];
4844 S->state[0] = in;
4845 S->state[2] = out;
4846
4847 /* return to application */
4848 return (out);
4849}
4850
4851
4867CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q15_t arm_pid_q15(
4868 arm_pid_instance_q15* S,
4869 q15_t in)
4870{
4871 q63_t acc;
4872 q15_t out;
4873
4874#if defined (ARM_MATH_DSP)
4875 __SIMD32_TYPE* vstate;
4876
4877 /* Implementation of PID controller */
4878
4879 /* acc = A0 * x[n] */
4880 acc = (q31_t) __SMUAD((uint32_t)S->A0, (uint32_t)in);
4881
4882 /* acc += A1 * x[n-1] + A2 * x[n-2] */
4883 vstate = __SIMD32_CONST(S->state);
4884 acc = (q63_t)__SMLALD((uint32_t)S->A1, (uint32_t) * vstate, (uint64_t)acc);
4885#else
4886 /* acc = A0 * x[n] */
4887 acc = ((q31_t) S->A0) * in;
4888
4889 /* acc += A1 * x[n-1] + A2 * x[n-2] */
4890 acc += (q31_t) S->A1 * S->state[0];
4891 acc += (q31_t) S->A2 * S->state[1];
4892#endif
4893
4894 /* acc += y[n-1] */
4895 acc += (q31_t) S->state[2] << 15;
4896
4897 /* saturate the output */
4898 out = (q15_t) (__SSAT((acc >> 15), 16));
4899
4900 /* Update state */
4901 S->state[1] = S->state[0];
4902 S->state[0] = in;
4903 S->state[2] = out;
4904
4905 /* return to application */
4906 return (out);
4907}

4978CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE void arm_clarke_f32(
4979 float32_t Ia,
4980 float32_t Ib,
4981 float32_t* pIalpha,
4982 float32_t* pIbeta)
4983{
4984 /* Calculate pIalpha using the equation, pIalpha = Ia */
4985 *pIalpha = Ia;
4986
4987 /* Calculate pIbeta using the equation, pIbeta = (1/sqrt(3)) * Ia + (2/sqrt(3)) * Ib */
4988 *pIbeta = ((float32_t) 0.57735026919 * Ia + (float32_t) 1.15470053838 * Ib);
4989}

5005CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE void arm_clarke_q31(
5006 q31_t Ia,
5007 q31_t Ib,
5008 q31_t* pIalpha,
5009 q31_t* pIbeta)
5010{
5011 q31_t product1, product2; /* Temporary variables used to store intermediate results */
5012
5013 /* Calculating pIalpha from Ia by equation pIalpha = Ia */
5014 *pIalpha = Ia;
5015
5016 /* Intermediate product is calculated by (1/(sqrt(3)) * Ia) */
5017 product1 = (q31_t) (((q63_t) Ia * 0x24F34E8B) >> 30);
5018
5019 /* Intermediate product is calculated by (2/sqrt(3) * Ib) */
5020 product2 = (q31_t) (((q63_t) Ib * 0x49E69D16) >> 30);
5021
5022 /* pIbeta is calculated by adding the intermediate products */
5023 *pIbeta = __QADD(product1, product2);
5024}

5216CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE void arm_park_q31(

5225 q31_t product3, product4; /* Temporary variables used to store intermediate results */
5226

5228 product1 = (q31_t) (((q63_t) (Ialpha) * (cosVal)) >> 31);

5231 product2 = (q31_t) (((q63_t) (Ibeta) * (sinVal)) >> 31);

5424CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE float32_t arm_linear_interp_f32(
5425 arm_linear_interp_instance_f32* S,
5426 float32_t x)
5427{
5428 float32_t y;
5429 float32_t x0, x1; /* Nearest input values */
5430 float32_t y0, y1; /* Nearest output values */
5431 float32_t xSpacing = S->xSpacing; /* spacing between input values */
5432 int32_t i; /* Index variable */
5433 float32_t* pYData = S->pYData; /* pointer to output table */
5434
5435 /* Calculation of index */
5436 i = (int32_t) ((x - S->x1) / xSpacing);
5437
5438 if (i < 0) {
5439 /* Iniatilize output for below specified range as least output value of table */
5440 y = pYData[0];
5441 }
5442 else if ((uint32_t)i >= S->nValues) {
5443 /* Iniatilize output for above specified range as last output value of table */
5444 y = pYData[S->nValues - 1];
5445 }
5446 else {
5447 /* Calculation of nearest input values */
5448 x0 = S->x1 + i * xSpacing;
5449 x1 = S->x1 + (i + 1) * xSpacing;
5450
5451 /* Read of nearest output values */
5452 y0 = pYData[i];
5453 y1 = pYData[i + 1];
5454
5455 /* Calculation of output */
5456 y = y0 + (x - x0) * ((y1 - y0) / (x1 - x0));
5457
5458 }
5459
5460 /* returns output value */
5461 return (y);
5462}

5464
5478CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q31_t arm_linear_interp_q31(
5479 q31_t* pYData,
5480 q31_t x,
5481 uint32_t nValues)
5482{
5483 q31_t y; /* output */
5484 q31_t y0, y1; /* Nearest output values */
5485 q31_t fract; /* fractional part */
5486 int32_t index; /* Index to read nearest output values */
5487
5488 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
5489 /* 12 bits for the table index */
5490 /* Index value calculation */
5491 index = ((x & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
5492
5493 if (index >= (int32_t)(nValues - 1)) {
5494 return (pYData[nValues - 1]);
5495 }
5496 else if (index < 0) {
5497 return (pYData[0]);
5498 }
5499 else {
5500 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
5501 /* shift left by 11 to keep fract in 1.31 format */
5502 fract = (x & 0x000FFFFF) << 11;
5503
5504 /* Read two nearest output values from the index in 1.31(q31) format */
5505 y0 = pYData[index];
5506 y1 = pYData[index + 1];
5507
5508 /* Calculation of y0 * (1-fract) and y is in 2.30 format */
5509 y = ((q31_t) ((q63_t) y0 * (0x7FFFFFFF - fract) >> 32));
5510
5511 /* Calculation of y0 * (1-fract) + y1 *fract and y is in 2.30 format */
5512 y += ((q31_t) (((q63_t) y1 * fract) >> 32));
5513
5514 /* Convert y to 1.31 format */
5515 return (y << 1u);
5516 }
5517}

5533CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q15_t arm_linear_interp_q15(
5534 q15_t* pYData,
5535 q31_t x,
5536 uint32_t nValues)
5537{
5538 q63_t y; /* output */
5539 q15_t y0, y1; /* Nearest output values */
5540 q31_t fract; /* fractional part */
5541 int32_t index; /* Index to read nearest output values */
5542
5543 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
5544 /* 12 bits for the table index */
5545 /* Index value calculation */
5546 index = ((x & (int32_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
5547
5548 if (index >= (int32_t)(nValues - 1)) {
5549 return (pYData[nValues - 1]);
5550 }
5551 else if (index < 0) {
5552 return (pYData[0]);
5553 }
5554 else {
5555 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
5556 /* fract is in 12.20 format */
5557 fract = (x & 0x000FFFFF);
5558
5559 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
5560 y0 = pYData[index];
5561 y1 = pYData[index + 1];
5562
5563 /* Calculation of y0 * (1-fract) and y is in 13.35 format */
5564 y = ((q63_t) y0 * (0xFFFFF - fract));
5565
5566 /* Calculation of (y0 * (1-fract) + y1 * fract) and y is in 13.35 format */
5567 y += ((q63_t) y1 * (fract));
5568
5569 /* convert y to 1.15 format */
5570 return (q15_t) (y >> 20);
5571 }
5572}

5587CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q7_t arm_linear_interp_q7(
5588 q7_t* pYData,
5589 q31_t x,
5590 uint32_t nValues)
5591{
5592 q31_t y; /* output */
5593 q7_t y0, y1; /* Nearest output values */
5594 q31_t fract; /* fractional part */
5595 uint32_t index; /* Index to read nearest output values */
5596
5597 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
5598 /* 12 bits for the table index */
5599 /* Index value calculation */
5600 if (x < 0) {
5601 return (pYData[0]);
5602 }
5603 index = (x >> 20) & 0xfff;
5604
5605 if (index >= (nValues - 1)) {
5606 return (pYData[nValues - 1]);
5607 }
5608 else {
5609 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
5610 /* fract is in 12.20 format */
5611 fract = (x & 0x000FFFFF);
5612
5613 /* Read two nearest output values from the index and are in 1.7(q7) format */
5614 y0 = pYData[index];
5615 y1 = pYData[index + 1];
5616
5617 /* Calculation of y0 * (1-fract ) and y is in 13.27(q27) format */
5618 y = ((y0 * (0xFFFFF - fract)));
5619
5620 /* Calculation of y1 * fract + y0 * (1-fract) and y is in 13.27(q27) format */
5621 y += (y1 * fract);
5622
5623 /* convert y to 1.7(q7) format */
5624 return (q7_t) (y >> 20);
5625 }
5626}

5782CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE void arm_circularWrite_f32(
5783 int32_t* circBuffer,
5784 int32_t L,
5785 uint16_t* writeOffset,
5786 int32_t bufferInc,
5787 const int32_t* src,
5788 int32_t srcInc,
5789 uint32_t blockSize)
5790{
5791 uint32_t i = 0u;
5792 int32_t wOffset;
5793
5794 /* Copy the value of Index pointer that points
5795 * to the current location where the input samples to be copied */
5796 wOffset = *writeOffset;
5797
5798 /* Loop over the blockSize */
5799 i = blockSize;
5800
5801 while (i > 0u) {
5802 /* copy the input sample to the circular buffer */
5803 circBuffer[wOffset] = *src;
5804
5805 /* Update the input pointer */
5806 src += srcInc;
5807
5808 /* Circularly update wOffset. Watch out for positive and negative value */
5809 wOffset += bufferInc;
5810 if (wOffset >= L)
5811 wOffset -= L;
5812
5813 /* Decrement the loop counter */
5814 i--;
5815 }
5816
5817 /* Update the index pointer */
5818 *writeOffset = (uint16_t)wOffset;
5819}

5991 i = blockSize;
5992
5993 while (i > 0u) {
5994 /* copy the input sample to the circular buffer */
5995 circBuffer[wOffset] = *src;
5996
5997 /* Update the input pointer */
5998 src += srcInc;
5999
6000 /* Circularly update wOffset. Watch out for positive and negative value */
6001 wOffset += bufferInc;
6002 if (wOffset >= L)
6003 wOffset -= L;
6004
6005 /* Decrement the loop counter */
6006 i--;
6007 }
6008
6009 /* Update the index pointer */
6010 *writeOffset = (uint16_t)wOffset;
6011}

6017CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE void arm_circularRead_q7(
6018 q7_t* circBuffer,
6019 int32_t L,
6020 int32_t* readOffset,
6021 int32_t bufferInc,
6022 q7_t* dst,
6023 q7_t* dst_base,
6024 int32_t dst_length,
6025 int32_t dstInc,
6026 uint32_t blockSize)
6027{
6028 uint32_t i = 0;
6029 int32_t rOffset, dst_end;
6030
6031 /* Copy the value of Index pointer that points
6032 * to the current location from where the input samples to be read */
6033 rOffset = *readOffset;
6034
6035 dst_end = (int32_t) (dst_base + dst_length);
6036
6037 /* Loop over the blockSize */
6038 i = blockSize;
6039
6040 while (i > 0u) {
6041 /* copy the sample from the circular buffer to the destination buffer */
6042 *dst = circBuffer[rOffset];
6043
6044 /* Update the input pointer */
6045 dst += dstInc;
6046
6047 if (dst == (q7_t*) dst_end) {
6048 dst = dst_base;
6049 }
6050
6051 /* Circularly update rOffset. Watch out for positive and negative value */
6052 rOffset += bufferInc;
6053
6054 if (rOffset >= L) {
6055 rOffset -= L;
6056 }
6057
6058 /* Decrement the loop counter */
6059 i--;
6060 }
6061
6062 /* Update the index pointer */
6063 *readOffset = rOffset;
6064}

6717CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE float32_t arm_bilinear_interp_f32(
6718 const arm_bilinear_interp_instance_f32* S,
6719 float32_t X,
6720 float32_t Y)
6721{
6722 float32_t out;
6723 float32_t f00, f01, f10, f11;
6724 float32_t* pData = S->pData;
6725 int32_t xIndex, yIndex, index;
6726 float32_t xdiff, ydiff;
6727 float32_t b1, b2, b3, b4;
6728
6729 xIndex = (int32_t) X;
6730 yIndex = (int32_t) Y;
6731
6732 /* Care taken for table outside boundary */
6733 /* Returns zero output when values are outside table boundary */
6734 if (xIndex < 0 || xIndex > (S->numRows - 1) || yIndex < 0 || yIndex > (S->numCols - 1)) {
6735 return (0);
6736 }
6737
6738 /* Calculation of index for two nearest points in X-direction */
6739 index = (xIndex - 1) + (yIndex - 1) * S->numCols;
6740
6741
6742 /* Read two nearest points in X-direction */
6743 f00 = pData[index];
6744 f01 = pData[index + 1];
6745
6746 /* Calculation of index for two nearest points in Y-direction */
6747 index = (xIndex - 1) + (yIndex) * S->numCols;
6748
6749
6750 /* Read two nearest points in Y-direction */
6751 f10 = pData[index];
6752 f11 = pData[index + 1];
6753
6754 /* Calculation of intermediate values */
6755 b1 = f00;
6756 b2 = f01 - f00;
6757 b3 = f10 - f00;
6758 b4 = f00 - f01 - f10 + f11;
6759
6760 /* Calculation of fractional part in X */
6761 xdiff = X - xIndex;
6762
6763 /* Calculation of fractional part in Y */
6764 ydiff = Y - yIndex;
6765
6766 /* Calculation of bi-linear interpolated output */
6767 out = b1 + b2 * xdiff + b3 * ydiff + b4 * xdiff * ydiff;
6768
6769 /* return to application */
6770 return (out);
6771}

6782CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q31_t arm_bilinear_interp_q31(
6783 arm_bilinear_interp_instance_q31* S,
6784 q31_t X,
6785 q31_t Y)
6786{
6787 q31_t out; /* Temporary output */
6788 q31_t acc = 0; /* output */
6789 q31_t xfract, yfract; /* X, Y fractional parts */
6790 q31_t x1, x2, y1, y2; /* Nearest output values */
6791 int32_t rI, cI; /* Row and column indices */
6792 q31_t* pYData = S->pData; /* pointer to output table values */
6793 uint32_t nCols = S->numCols; /* num of rows */
6794
6795 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
6796 /* 12 bits for the table index */
6797 /* Index value calculation */
6798 rI = ((X & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6799
6800 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
6801 /* 12 bits for the table index */
6802 /* Index value calculation */
6803 cI = ((Y & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6804
6805 /* Care taken for table outside boundary */
6806 /* Returns zero output when values are outside table boundary */
6807 if (rI < 0 || rI > (S->numRows - 1) || cI < 0 || cI > (S->numCols - 1)) {
6808 return (0);
6809 }
6810
6811 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
6812 /* shift left xfract by 11 to keep 1.31 format */
6813 xfract = (X & 0x000FFFFF) << 11u;
6814
6815 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
6816 x1 = pYData[(rI) + (int32_t)nCols * (cI) ];
6817 x2 = pYData[(rI) + (int32_t)nCols * (cI) + 1];
6818
6819 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
6820 /* shift left yfract by 11 to keep 1.31 format */
6821 yfract = (Y & 0x000FFFFF) << 11u;
6822
6823 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
6824 y1 = pYData[(rI) + (int32_t)nCols * (cI + 1) ];
6825 y2 = pYData[(rI) + (int32_t)nCols * (cI + 1) + 1];
6826
6827 /* Calculation of x1 * (1-xfract ) * (1-yfract) and acc is in 3.29(q29) format */
6828 out = ((q31_t) (((q63_t) x1 * (0x7FFFFFFF - xfract)) >> 32));
6829 acc = ((q31_t) (((q63_t) out * (0x7FFFFFFF - yfract)) >> 32));
6830
6831 /* x2 * (xfract) * (1-yfract) in 3.29(q29) and adding to acc */
6832 out = ((q31_t) ((q63_t) x2 * (0x7FFFFFFF - yfract) >> 32));
6833 acc += ((q31_t) ((q63_t) out * (xfract) >> 32));
6834
6835 /* y1 * (1 - xfract) * (yfract) in 3.29(q29) and adding to acc */
6836 out = ((q31_t) ((q63_t) y1 * (0x7FFFFFFF - xfract) >> 32));
6837 acc += ((q31_t) ((q63_t) out * (yfract) >> 32));
6838
6839 /* y2 * (xfract) * (yfract) in 3.29(q29) and adding to acc */
6840 out = ((q31_t) ((q63_t) y2 * (xfract) >> 32));
6841 acc += ((q31_t) ((q63_t) out * (yfract) >> 32));
6842
6843 /* Convert acc to 1.31(q31) format */
6844 return ((q31_t)(acc << 2));
6845}

6855CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q15_t arm_bilinear_interp_q15(
6856 arm_bilinear_interp_instance_q15* S,
6857 q31_t X,
6858 q31_t Y)
6859{
6860 q63_t acc = 0; /* output */
6861 q31_t out; /* Temporary output */
6862 q15_t x1, x2, y1, y2; /* Nearest output values */
6863 q31_t xfract, yfract; /* X, Y fractional parts */
6864 int32_t rI, cI; /* Row and column indices */
6865 q15_t* pYData = S->pData; /* pointer to output table values */
6866 uint32_t nCols = S->numCols; /* num of rows */
6867
6868 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
6869 /* 12 bits for the table index */
6870 /* Index value calculation */
6871 rI = ((X & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6872
6873 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
6874 /* 12 bits for the table index */
6875 /* Index value calculation */
6876 cI = ((Y & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6877
6878 /* Care taken for table outside boundary */
6879 /* Returns zero output when values are outside table boundary */
6880 if (rI < 0 || rI > (S->numRows - 1) || cI < 0 || cI > (S->numCols - 1)) {
6881 return (0);
6882 }
6883
6884 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
6885 /* xfract should be in 12.20 format */
6886 xfract = (X & 0x000FFFFF);
6887
6888 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
6889 x1 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI) ];
6890 x2 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI) + 1];
6891
6892 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
6893 /* yfract should be in 12.20 format */
6894 yfract = (Y & 0x000FFFFF);
6895
6896 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
6897 y1 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI + 1) ];
6898 y2 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI + 1) + 1];
6899
6900 /* Calculation of x1 * (1-xfract ) * (1-yfract) and acc is in 13.51 format */
6901
6902 /* x1 is in 1.15(q15), xfract in 12.20 format and out is in 13.35 format */
6903 /* convert 13.35 to 13.31 by right shifting and out is in 1.31 */
6904 out = (q31_t) (((q63_t) x1 * (0xFFFFF - xfract)) >> 4u);
6905 acc = ((q63_t) out * (0xFFFFF - yfract));
6906
6907 /* x2 * (xfract) * (1-yfract) in 1.51 and adding to acc */
6908 out = (q31_t) (((q63_t) x2 * (0xFFFFF - yfract)) >> 4u);
6909 acc += ((q63_t) out * (xfract));
6910
6911 /* y1 * (1 - xfract) * (yfract) in 1.51 and adding to acc */
6912 out = (q31_t) (((q63_t) y1 * (0xFFFFF - xfract)) >> 4u);
6913 acc += ((q63_t) out * (yfract));
6914
6915 /* y2 * (xfract) * (yfract) in 1.51 and adding to acc */
6916 out = (q31_t) (((q63_t) y2 * (xfract)) >> 4u);
6917 acc += ((q63_t) out * (yfract));
6918
6919 /* acc is in 13.51 format and down shift acc by 36 times */
6920 /* Convert out to 1.15 format */
6921 return ((q15_t)(acc >> 36));
6922}

6932CMSIS_INLINE __STATIC_INLINE q7_t arm_bilinear_interp_q7(
6933 arm_bilinear_interp_instance_q7* S,

6937 q63_t acc = 0; /* output */
6938 q31_t out; /* Temporary output */
6939 q31_t xfract, yfract; /* X, Y fractional parts */
6940 q7_t x1, x2, y1, y2; /* Nearest output values */
6941 int32_t rI, cI; /* Row and column indices */
6942 q7_t* pYData = S->pData; /* pointer to output table values */
6943 uint32_t nCols = S->numCols; /* num of rows */
6944
6945 /* Input is in 12.20 format */
6946 /* 12 bits for the table index */

6948 rI = ((X & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6949

6951 /* 12 bits for the table index */
6952 /* Index value calculation */
6953 cI = ((Y & (q31_t)0xFFF00000) >> 20);
6954
6955 /* Care taken for table outside boundary */
6956 /* Returns zero output when values are outside table boundary */
6957 if (rI < 0 || rI > (S->numRows - 1) || cI < 0 || cI > (S->numCols - 1)) {
6958 return (0);
6959 }
6960
6961 /* 20 bits for the fractional part */
6962 /* xfract should be in 12.20 format */
6963 xfract = (X & (q31_t)0x000FFFFF);
6964
6965 /* Read two nearest output values from the index */
6966 x1 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI) ];
6967 x2 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI) + 1];
6968

6970 /* yfract should be in 12.20 format */
6971 yfract = (Y & (q31_t)0x000FFFFF);

6975 y2 = pYData[((uint32_t)rI) + nCols * ((uint32_t)cI + 1) + 1];
6976

6978 out = ((x1 * (0xFFFFF - xfract)));
6979 acc = (((q63_t) out * (0xFFFFF - yfract)));
6980

6982 out = ((x2 * (0xFFFFF - yfract)));

6986 out = ((y1 * (0xFFFFF - xfract)));
6987 acc += (((q63_t) out * (yfract)));
6988
6989 /* y2 * (xfract) * (yfract) in 2.22 and adding to acc */
6990 out = ((y2 * (yfract)));
6991 acc += (((q63_t) out * (xfract)));
6992
6993 /* acc in 16.47 format and down shift by 40 to convert to 1.7 format */
6994 return ((q7_t)(acc >> 40));
6995}
